She sees HotRod walk right past her and go to the brig.
She shrugged her shoulders, put her gun away and walked back to her 
room.  She slammed the door again as hard as she could.  She looked 
around the room.  She slammed her fist into the wall and heard a loud 
bang as her hand made contact with the metal wall.
